<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.5">
<l>māka mānilam muḻutumvan tiraiñcum malara ṭikaṇṭa māmaṟai yāḷaṉ</l>
<l>tōkai māmayi laṉṉava riṉpan tuṟṟi lāmaiyi lattaviṅ koḻintu</l>
<l>pōkam nīyeytip piṉṉunam miṭaikkē pōtu vāyeṉṟa poṉṉaru ḷeṉakkum</l>
<l>āka vēṇṭumeṉ ṟaṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkattam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[To] a great master of the Vedas, who saw your flower-like feet</l>
<l rend="indent">where the whole great earth and heavens came and worshipped,</l>
<l>Since [he] was lacking [any] enjoyment of delight,</l>
<l rend="indent">such as [that of] a great, plumed peacock, [you] said,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Father, having remained here, gaining pleasures,</l>
<l>You come to  us later”; thinking that [I] need the [same] precious grace</l>
<l rend="indent">to happen to me, too,</l>
<l>I took refuge at your two feet, lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
